name: Voxed Stars Spaceman 100 Edition Holder
description:
This was given to those that had collected 100 Spacemen or more by 10/31/2021 
Thank you for your time and support, you are the foundation of Voxed Stars. It's because of collectors like you that I can keep making Voxed Stars. Keep Vibin. 

Special shout out to Edogxx for being the first to join us on this journey and putting in the time to buy 100 of these Space men. Big props to you sir, your dedication is appreciated. Big Thank you to John for being a loyal friend and collector. Now buckle up, because we are headed to the moon.
